title: Open-Menu-Group Chat
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Staging
2. When User Click GroupChat Menu
3. Then Close Webs

title: Send-Message
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Staging
2. When User Click GroupChat Menu
3. And User Input Message
4. And User Click Submit Button
5. Then Close Webs

title: Mention-Member
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Staging
2. When User Click GroupChat Menu
3. And User Input Message
4. And User Input @ Message
5. And User Click People in shown
6. And User Click Submit Button
7. Then Close Webs

title: Upload-File
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Staging
2. When User Click GroupChat Menu
3. And User Upload Attachment
4. Then Close Webs

title: Send-Empty-Message
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Staging
2. When User Click GroupChat Menu
3. And User Click Submit Button
4. Then Close Webs
